source_text:
Generate the wooden crafting recipes of a mod in the Corail Woodcutter format in your config folder
 /woodcutter info
 /woodcutter datapack [generate|apply|remove] <modid>
apply & remove are useable in singleplayer and the datapack must be generated before applying it
